name: POS Fuel
description: This beverage has an off grey color reminiscent of dirty dish water, with a fruity taste that makes it easy to forget how much alcohol you are consuming. It was invented by the legendary outlaw <url=showinfo:1377//1119812570>Verone</url> and popularized by the Guristas-aligned capsuleer pirates of the <url=showinfo:2//695264821>Veto.</url> corporation. It has since become a staple libation at underground pirate gatherings across New Eden.
